Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:03.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the god of this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:08.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She found herself on an island when she began to understand things around her."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:11.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"There was no one else there."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She had nothing to do."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:15.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"That was the everything the world offered."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:14.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How much have you written?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't written much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:19.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Probably only about thirty percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I can't do much alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can I look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:28.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"One day the girl made a fire at the beach."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:35.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"That was because there was a scene in a book where a stranded person made a fire."{That is because in one of the book there was a story about human making fire and something}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:39.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"In the deep blue sky, a straight white road climbed up."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:42.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She thought, 'Maybe it's the same as the cloud."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:46.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"So she put her head in it, and her mouth and eyes became really painful."{[Again, on = in?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:50.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"In haste, she moved away and gazed at it from a distance."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:54.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She then understands that it is useless to her."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:57.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Just like that, she begins to understand things one by one."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:01.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She understood the meaning of understanding."{[comprehension]}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:04.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:10.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She is... cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:13.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should rewrite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,From where?{[Not sure if this is right, but it seems to be it just doesn't fit in the context. -Xien]}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everything until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:21.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because you said she was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:25.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just thinking she shouldn't be thought of that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:30.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With this short of an episode, it'll be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You are mistaken, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:37.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This girl should be more of a peculiar person.{something} {check, I hear tsureteru, that's like taken away or something? maybe have another word for it but I cant think of one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:42.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She'll hear a joke and take it very seriously.{When she jokes, people will think she is serious.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:46.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The readers need to feel worried and uneasy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:51.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If she is said to be cute, then I must not have written her existence properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a bento?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Also for Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?{No one said I couldn't.}{check} {I cant think of another words} {...Original written line was "No one says I can't." This may need a tl check anyways, but for now, I've put the sentence into proper english. -- Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:05.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Being good at cooking will be helpful as a spouse,{Good at cooking will be helpful as a house-husband,}{housewife}{[Having good culinary skills...? -Xien]}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,but it would complicate things.{be complicated as a mother. [complicate things -Xien]}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:14.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because if you are better than your girlfriend, then she can't make a bento for you with love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You and Chihiro aren't a couple?{You are not a couple with Chihiro-chan? [Would "You two aren't a couple?" sound better?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a carefree person.{What a carefree person.}{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:29.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess you want no one else but me to be your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous... I said that's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:39.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?{Is there something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about my future career.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Future career?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:48.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a questionnaire about what you want to be in the future. {[on a questionnaire?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There is this future career questionnaire at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?{Is there something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should write.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:08.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should just put whatever you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:11.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I had an idea, then I wouldn't be troubled like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:13.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm like this but I don't really have any talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at cooking, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:28.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:31.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:33.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are doing this regularly. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You mean making lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Is it for Chihiro-chan again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:40.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big help that you're making breakfast too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two still aren't a couple yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:49.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:53.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that your reaction didn't seem to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:54.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:06:01.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just a hypothetical situation, but if Chihiro and I were to become a couple, would you be happy?{Hey, just a hypothetical situation, but if me and Chihiro become a couple, will you become happy?}{...Yeah, changing "an if" to "a hypothetical". - Waku} {Hey, just a hypothetical situation, but if Chihiro and I were to become a couple, would you become happy? -Xien}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having fun being with Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,T-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:14.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to get angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:17.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm getting angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:23.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You are a man, so you should practice going out with responsibility.{[going out responsibly?  or is it "... so you should practice going out with responsibility"? -Xien *check*]}{Gamefish - Name doesn't have to be included here. Otherwise it would be at the end of the sentence.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a downward hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Once it starts, it can't be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:30.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But affection is a rising affair.  {koi}{Aiko: I think she means something like a lasting relationship or true love, something sappy like that. I think she says "Ai" here...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:34.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You have to climb with the painful and difficult times together. {[You can't 'climb' times. You can go through them, but not climb them. Unless it was in the actual line... -Xien]}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:41.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but the hardships are with the ones that you like, whereas being with the one that you love is something that cannot be stopped.{Ah, but the hardship is with your [sweetheart][koi] and the one cannot be stopped is with your lover[Does this make sense? -Xien]}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess they go against each other.{[they're against each other?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:48.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they are just like tofu and nattou, something of a paradox.{something, nattou} {check} {...I 'm pretty sure she mentioned tofu somewhere in there... How did this turn into a conversation on food? O_o;;; -- Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:56.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She painted a human being..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:07:00.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl painted a figure of a boy."{man"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:06.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"So, she decided to add a figure of a boy into paintings of landscapes she had painted."{And then she redrew the scenery she had drawn with that bo included.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:10.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"With no specific reason, she kept those paintings in the same places where she painted them."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Soon, there was not a single place on that island she did not paint."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:17.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She was always with the boy everywhere she went."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:21.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"It meant that the girl and boy looked at each other every time she looked at the paintings."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:26.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"However, the girl had no feeling of achievement."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:30.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Would it be a 'human?', she thought."{Is this a human? She thought.["Is this human?" she thought]}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:34.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"This was the 'painting of a human being.' "{No, this is a human painting.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:37.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"He did not move nor think. He was simply there."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:43.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Lonely? Finally, she could ask herself by finding the word."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She was not lonely."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:53.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With this, aren't you about seventy percent done?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:56.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think it should be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:58.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought about the ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now, there are two main ideas for the end of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:12.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,First would be that the girl went into the paintings and lived happily ever after with the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a fantasy story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:18.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Second would be that the boy in the paintings became a real boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:22.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how it should end but I think it should be at least a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:28.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's really up to one's wish on having either a happy or sad ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:31.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:38.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell the story about going into the paintings as a fantasy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:44.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you can also say the girl is trying to run away from reality due to loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:51.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can also think that due to loneliness the girl ran away from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:54.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she's broken, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:02.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on one's interpretation, but yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that was my comment for this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I think she is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:12.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She has to remember about loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {I guess Renji is writing how many times they had the same conversation before.}{This is kinda lame.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:19.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's somehow bad deciding the ending this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:24.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because it feels like God is tampering with it.{Because it feels like you're playing God.} {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can really do it when I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:35.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized it, we had been talking for so long. It's so enjoyable. {When I realized it, we had talked consistently? Dunno, but it sounds weird.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:43.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because now I've realized that I really can't do anything by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:54.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:55.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Err, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:11.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:24.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:29.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, do you... want to kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you... want to kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:40.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're doing this because someone told you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:46.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't think I've ever met anyone I've been as close to as Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:53.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I also think the reason I kept meeting with Renji-kun until now is because I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:59.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems that you like me too, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:04.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can kiss me like we're lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:09.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think the setting should be like this. {"I think the setting scene should be like this"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I getting confused?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:21.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I thinking that Chihiro is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:26.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If she is said to be cute, then I must not have written her existence properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:30.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This girl should be more of a peculiar person{something}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wrong! {the text is also "wrong"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:38.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is Chihiro not happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is she not feeling embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is she not writing about her facial expressions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:54.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is she not writing a single word about liking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:01.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's because God is tampering with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:12.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:36.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't... write that in your diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:40.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... don't write it. {better sentence} {[Seriously... don't write it. :o]}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:46.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong... everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the god of this world."{[That makes her the god of this world]}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:03.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wouldn't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:19.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wouldn't be able to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:27.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I had given up hope, but now I've found it. {[I had given up hope for it?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is... a place where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:37.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, maybe I was too daring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'll stimulate Hirono-kun too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, tomorrow's preparations...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a place where the sounds have disappeared. {" where there is no sound" etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day my mother disappeared from my father's heart. {mum dad?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My father also disappeared from my mother's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ma-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since then, the house has lost its noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:56.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since then, the house has lost its conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:01.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the color has since disappeared from my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:09.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without realizing it, even I disappeared from their hearts. {Aiko: Try the word "I" instead of me} {Accepted! -- Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:15.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since then, I had been living an empty life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've finally found a world with voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've found a space not lacking colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:43.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have to keep it buried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:48.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I am not able to answer the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:52.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When you hear the "beep", please leave your name and message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:55.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo, Hirono-kun? It's Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be at the place we promised for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it a feeding battle royal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The laws of nature sure are strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:27.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already there, are you on your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:29.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you if you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're late you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:41.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You should come ten minutes early for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:44.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not making the woman wait is the man's responsibility, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, late, late, late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to make me wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Today is going to be all on you, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here, so hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:04.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you are, then I'm not going to let you off that easily. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-ro-no-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're still not on your way? {coming}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How many hours are you going to make me wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even planning to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:38.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will erase your existence from Onii-chan's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, farewell to you.{Then I will just forget and say goodbye to you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And then, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will make it end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to disappear again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:59.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get the meeting place wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:02.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bench in front of the fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know where, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:07.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, then just call me and I'll come and get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you didn't get into anything bad on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Call me when you get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:23.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Call me now already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:32.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please answer the phone. I know you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You are listening to this now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the phone. Let's have a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you answering the phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you answering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you not saying anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:53.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen and contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not angry or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:58.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting here until we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting until I hear something from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:05.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:06.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Come here and meet me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:09.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you only show your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you only let me hear anything from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:19.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, you are coming here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:22.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can keep on waiting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:26.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe you... I'll believe in you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:29.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Send me a mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,or just a comment, it's fine... {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please... don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:46.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:59.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you don't want to come after all? {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me, Hirono-kun?{Am I being hated by you, Hirono-kun?} {better sentence }
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:06.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If so, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate me, then please say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just be silent, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:16.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please I beg you, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:23.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for saying such strange things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:26.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're angry... You're angry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,and I do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And I just pull you around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:35.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:43.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking forward so much to the date today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:50.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was very excited when I thought about you, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time feeling this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:56.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:58.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you, Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:10.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:17.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to... disappear from your heart, Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:57.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:22:58.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing really serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:03.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the convenience store, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Garibori-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:05.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I mean for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:07.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I make something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:08.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.58,0:23:09.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's really mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:13.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I may be like this, but I'm practicing cooking now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:15.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When you don't need anymore practice, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:17.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Should I just buy whatever looks good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:18.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:24.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What, it's here-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.38,0:23:34.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Messages deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:37.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A color without hues...{Try something poetic despite the oxymoron like "Color without hue" or something stupid like that}{Works.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:39.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,is pure and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:43.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Next {\i1}ef - a tale of memories{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:44.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Clear Colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:47.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
